snippet.title: Greed of Man 0.7.1 Trailer
snippet.description: Greed of Man is an open world massive multiplayer crime simulator where you run illegal and legal businesses alone or with your friends. You can drive cars, mine for resources, participate in raids, sell your items on a fluctuating market. There is so much to do in this new Free Steam Game.
